Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:06.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:09.12,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:17.14,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:26.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.58,0:00:30.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:35.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:41.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:48.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.12,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:55.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:01:03.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:16.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:21.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:28.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:35.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:39.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.59,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:46.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.35,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:59.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:05.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:12.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:18.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:32.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this world \Nhas to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto theGrand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.56,0:03:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come on board, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Board my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have much choice \Nbut to help you guys out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Franky, will be the shipwright on your ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we said all sorts of things\Nto each other, we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let these little things go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...let me say one last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being bullheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.62,0:04:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab my hand already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think about this\Nfor the ship's name, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It consumes three barrels of cola,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it lets us fly one kilometer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing the Going Merry\Ncould do that this ship can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It exceeds the Merry in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Merry's brave soul will be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inherited by the Thousand Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Robin and Usopp, who came back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to our new friend, Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and to our pirate ship, the Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next destination is Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Vigaro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, are you looking at your\Ncollection by yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were awfully quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get started\Non the preparations now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure that you have\Na special birthday, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swap out with me, Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Mysterious Band of Pirates!\NSunny and the Dangerous Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats bathing in a massive\Ntub that sways on the waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This here is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What seems to be the problem?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll\Nget a patient anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I got a cool shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in! Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put it in the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.14,0:07:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In ya go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They dropped in another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a nice room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room's great,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't believe those \Nidiots tossed in a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check out the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did a shark come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an awesome one with horns!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it did, but you've lost all\Nof the other fish you caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about compatibility\N before you throw something in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a no-brainer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This punk's gonna be tonight's dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, roast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll barbecue that stupid shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a fresh fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should either make sushi or serve it\Nboiled with a hot and sour miso sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempura might be nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, thank you\Nfor this great ship, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no biggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still haven't seen\N its true power yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its true power?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship's key features are\N its "Soldier Dock System."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are five docks ranging from\NChannel 0 to Channel 4 located on the bilge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each dock is rigged to\Nhandle different situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them will play a unique role\Nin assisting the Thousand Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then lemme see them in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you see them as they're needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a shame to show them off all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo! Boo! Boo! Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it seemed a lot colder\Nthan yesterday, and I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we've entered\Na winter island's currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kokoro-san never mentioned\Nanything about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, it's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.61,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're spoiling the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you're supposed\Nto act when it snows:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.61,0:09:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Guys, it's snowing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you still didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really aren't that bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing ticks me off more than\Nhaving them call me names!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen snow in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should make something\Nwarm for dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something seems a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have any sails,\N let alone an ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have any sails?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means it's just floating there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either a ship in distress, or it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some pirates play a nasty game \Ncalled the "Davy Back Fight."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they fell victim to that game, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look horribly exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:11:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they end up being our enemy,\Nwe'll just send them flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any fish out there that'll\Nbite a hook without bait, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It beats doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got time to kill,\Nso let's be patient and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you guys all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Make a break for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rudder doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we don't have any sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, both you and your ship are\Nin sorry shape! You're both a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're just humble fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishermen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About three days ago, we were\Nattacked by an unidentified ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did they steal all\Nof our valuables and food,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they also trashed our sail\Nand destroyed our rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been floating out here ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got nothing to gain by attacking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, all of \Nyou are hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to eat, so come join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cook can't turn a blind \Neye to guys like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's just about ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been dying to get some patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go tend to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, let's have\Nanyone injured come see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone too badly hurt to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their pet just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worth a whopping 50 Berries! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose these are rookie\Npirates who just hit the seas
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with their new ship and stars still in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do things look over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, we're in the middle\Nof winning a pirate crew over...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,uh, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what does their\NJolly Roger look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's a skull wearing a straw hat, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you'd go hunting\Nfor bugs out on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could they be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make small talk with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now listen to me carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a total bounty of\N600 million Berries on their heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600 million, sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,0:14:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what you must do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all too well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't you dare let\Nthem escape before we arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600 million Berries on their heads...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too good, Mister Eyebrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good it's making me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they crying drunks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ladies sure are cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute you're making me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they were late to notice us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you leave to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, after seeing what you can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is someone else I'd like you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you follow me aboard our ship right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're headed straight \Nfor the New World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will think any less of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hell over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we've only heard rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly it's a horrible place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what the rumors claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out for myself if it's\Nlike hell when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've been\Nlooking after my men for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let show you my gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm their commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Stansen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my best brew,\Nwhich I had specially ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:16:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have a patient down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does\Nhe think he's taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His entire body is seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been days since the\Nlast time he was conscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.55,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to help him get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His wounds are festering!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let him get this bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I had a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe to move him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to begin the\N operation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has a unique flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you had booze, even though\Nyou didn't have anything to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wow, this is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like finding a port in a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really ought to do more to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really must drop by our port
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can thank you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Drop by our port"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you want us\N to take you there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one funny man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll take ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we visit any of the other islands,\Nit'll change our log's course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't it be fine if we leave\Nas soon as we drop them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in need of help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm glad you have such\Nan understanding captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you to get us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, they say that the people\Nyou travel with make the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd say we're due for another "cheers"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a hilarious captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we can do now is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't over the worst of it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not excited about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were such considerate guys, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the girls were cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a choice in the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lay claim to this amazing ship, I bet we could take them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to hand this ship over to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are merely going to carry out\Nwhatever missions they assign to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call this a "mission"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to steal this ship\N and prepare to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As things stand now, Vigaro will\Nnever be able to rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to argue \Namongst yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't like the direction\Nthis conversation's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Weren't you sound asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of anesthesia was so\Nstrong that I couldn't fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my cuisine with that nasty drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be prepared to\Npay for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of them can\Nhandle this on their own...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have managed to successfully\Ndrive the prey into a tight corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some rookies are currently\Nonboard their ship right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've proven surprisingly useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, if I may be so bold,\Nit's still too soon to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they have hooked a rather large fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A large fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his \NStraw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their total bounty comes to 660 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How appropriate\Nfor such a splendid day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.24,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! You can leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly, you know, this really--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Click.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:23:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect this to turn into quite the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it troublesome when\Nyou have unexpected guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can deal with guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't we completely\Nsurrounded by Navy ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem somewhat happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you this ship's super powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sunny's in a Pinch!\NRoar, Secret Super-Speed Mecha"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
